                        <li>Review the keywords that are spending the most money. Pause any that aren't relevant to people looking for office space to rent.</li>
                        <li>Implement "negative keywords" (e.g., 'jobs', 'free', 'reviews') to stop ads from showing to people with the wrong intent, saving money.</li>
