                        <li>The general "awareness" campaign is not very effective at getting clicks, which is common for this type of campaign. Its main goal was to build an audience.</li>
                        <li>Your organic (non-paid) posts are performing exceptionally well, with a very high engagement rate of 7.7%. Your followers are clearly interested in your content.</li>
