                    <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2 text-sm optimization-list">
                        <li>Since the survey was so successful, consider sending short, engaging polls or surveys more regularly to keep the audience involved.</li>
                        <li>Use the email newsletters to promote your best-performing blog posts and website pages to drive traffic back to the site.</li>
                        <li>Segment your email list based on who clicked what. For example, people who clicked on Strathclyde Park content could receive more targeted emails about that location.</li>
                    </ul>
